quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  6,125,"Namni Rabbiin isa qajeelchuu fedhe, qoma Isaa Islaamaaf bal’isa. Nama isa jallisuu fedhe immoo qoma isaa akkaan dhiphaa, rakkataa akka nama samii keessa ol koruu taasisa. Akka kanatti Rabbiin adabbii warra hin amanne irratti godha.",""
  6,126,"Kun qajeelaa haala ta’een karaa Gooftaa keetiiti. Ummata gorfamaniif mallattoo dhugaadhaan adda baafneerra.",""
  6,127,"Isaaniif Gooftaa isaanii bira ganda nagayaatu jira. Innis waan isaan dalagaa turaniif jecha gargaaraa isaaniiti.",""
  6,128,"Guyyaa hunda isaanii walitti qabee ""Yaa garee jinnootaa! Namoota daneeffattanii jirtu"" (jedhuun yaadadhu). Jaalalleen isaanii kan namoota irraa ta’an ""Gooftaa keenya! gariin keenya gariitti qanani'e; beellama keenya Ati nuuf beellamte geenyee jirra"" jedhu. ""Hanga Rabbiin fedhe malee Ibiddi qubannaa keessani isii keessatti hafoodha"" jedha. Dhugumatti Gooftaan kee ogeessa, beekaadha.",""
  6,129,"Akka kanatti garii miidhaa hojjattoota garii irratti moosifna. Waan isaan hojjataa turaniif jecha.",""
  6,130,"\"A yagraw n leonun d yimdanen, day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen segwen? Mmalen awen issekniyen iW, nedôen kwen $ef temlilit n wass nnwen agi\". Nnan d: \"ncehhed $ef yiman nne$\". T$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Cehhden $ef yiman nnsen ar nitni, s tidep, llan d ijehliyen.""Yaa garee jinniifi namaa! Sila ergamoonni isin irraa ta’an kan keeyyattoota kiyya isin irratti qara’aniifi qunnamtii guyyaa keessanii kana kan isin dinniinanu isinitti hin dhufnee?"\"A yagraw n leonun d yimdanen, day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen segwen? Mmalen awen issekniyen iW, nedôen kwen $ef temlilit n wass nnwen agi\". Nnan d: \"ncehhed $ef yiman nne$\". T$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Cehhden $ef yiman nnsen ar nitni, s tidep, llan d ijehliyen." (jedhamu). "\"A yagraw n leonun d yimdanen, day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen segwen? Mmalen awen issekniyen iW, nedôen kwen $ef temlilit n wass nnwen agi\". Nnan d: \"ncehhed $ef yiman nne$\". T$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Cehhden $ef yiman nnsen ar nitni, s tidep, llan d ijehliyen."Nuti lubbuulee keenya irratti ragaa baanee jirra"\"A yagraw n leonun d yimdanen, day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen segwen? Mmalen awen issekniyen iW, nedôen kwen $ef temlilit n wass nnwen agi\". Nnan d: \"ncehhed $ef yiman nne$\". T$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Cehhden $ef yiman nnsen ar nitni, s tidep, llan d ijehliyen." jedhan. Jireenyi addunyaa isaan gowwoomsite. Dhugumatti isaan kaafiroota akka turan lubbuulee isaanii irratti ragaa ba’an.","\"A yagraw n leonun d yimdanen, day ur kwen id usan ara imazanen segwen? Mmalen awen issekniyen iW, nedôen kwen $ef temlilit n wass nnwen agi\". Nnan d: \"ncehhed $ef yiman nne$\". T$uôô iten tmeddurt n ddunit. Cehhden $ef yiman nnsen ar nitni, s tidep, llan d ijehliyen."
  6,131,"Kun waan Gooftaan kee ganda tokko haala warri ishee dagataa ta'een, badii (isheetiif jecha) kan balleessu hin ta'iniifi.",""
